1 The General Assembly shall be required to hold a public hearing on the LRC's
2 recommendations within six months of receiving the final report, ensuring legislative
3 consideration and potential action on identified licensing reforms.
4 SECTION 4.1.(e) Effective Date. – This section is effective when it becomes law.
5 SECTION 5.1. Effective Dates. – Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective
6 when it becomes law.
